'''AudioOrbs''' is a PC-only audio visualization world, utilizing AudioLink. The world features thirty-two individual [[Community:AudioLink|AudioLink]] enabled orbs, that dynamically luminate the environment, and any avatars utilizing the AudioLink prefab.

